TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi beforefieldinit HttpFileCollectionWrapper extends System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase

Docs.summary: Encapsulates the HTTP intrinsic object that provides access to files that were uploaded by a client.

remarks.format: ## Remarks The <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionWrapper> class derives from the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase> class and serves as a wrapper for the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection> class. This class exposes the functionality of the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection> class while also exposing the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase> type. The <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollectionBase> class enables you to replace the original implementation of the <xref:System.Web.HttpFileCollection> class in your application with a custom implementation, such as when you perform unit testing outside the ASP.NET pipeline.
